      "id": "PopularPost305204",
      "post_content": "This is my favorite of the Ice Age (Ability. Draw a card at the beginning of the next turn's upkeep.) type cards. If they have 2 lands and a gimp card coming, you can choose to give them two lands and a gimp card last, or if it's hell coming you can shuffle and hope for the best. One blue for a draw is acceptable too.",
