      "id": "PopularPost361047",
      "post_content": "Being able to control someone's draws is a brutal bit of tech. I've always wanted to use this, [Misinformation](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Misinformation) and cards that mill just one card at time to build a deck where you constantly control their draws into continually more useless stuff.  \n  \nBetween counterspells and kill spells you can hold the early game while stuff like this tries to ensure there is never a late game. Sounds both obnoxious and fun to me!",
      "posted_by": "blurrymadness",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost361047\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Being able to control someone's draws is a brutal bit of tech. I've always wanted to use this, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Misinformation\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Misinformation\">Misinformation</a> and cards that mill just one card at time to build a deck where you constantly control their draws into continually more useless stuff.<br/><br/>Between counterspells and kill spells you can hold the early game while stuff like this tries to ensure there is never a late game. Sounds both obnoxious and fun to me!</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '361047'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy44651\">blurrymadness</span>\r\n                                (1/31/2014 11:39:24 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=